Name: Mini bobcat with wheels
Description: Compact zero-turn wheel loader that excels on concrete and asphalt. Ideal for site clean-ups, interior demolition, and landscaping where low ground disturbance matters. Includes general bucket; pallet forks available on request for moving blocks and pallets.

Name: Mini excavator
Description: Compact zero-tail mini excavator for tight access trenching, garden works, and small demolition. Rubber tracks protect paving while delivering confident digging for footings and services. Quick to transport and set up where larger machines will not fit.

Name: Medium Bobcat Skid Steer w/ tracks
Description: Track loader built for sand, clay, and uneven ground. Outstanding traction and stability for grading, backfilling, and moving bulk materials without tearing up the site. Pairs well with tooth bucket or forks for all-round site work.

Name: Larger Bobcat Skid Steer w/ tracks
Description: High-power track loader with strong hydraulics and lift for heavier pallets and bulk earthmoving. Excellent on steep or soft terrain, keeping productivity high in tough conditions. Choose it for demanding grading, pad prep, and material handling.

Name: Medium Excavator
Description: Mid-size excavator for deeper trenching, footings, and truck loading on medium sites. Longer reach and digging force than mini units while remaining compact enough for residential access. Balanced, fuel-efficient performance for all-day earthmoving.

Name: Large Excavator
Description: Heavy-duty excavator for major excavation, demolition, and site development. Strong breakout force and a stable footprint for confident digging and lifting. Ideal when you need reach, power, and consistent cycle times.

Name: Telehandler
Description: All-terrain telehandler for lifting and placing pallets to upper floors and rooflines. Precise boom control for safe loading at height on uneven ground. Perfect for masonry, timber, and steel deliveries across challenging sites.

Name: Compactor
Description: Reliable plate compactor for driveways, patios, and trench backfill. Produces dense, level surfaces quickly on soil, gravel, and asphalt repairs. Compact and easy to handle around forms and edges to speed up small works.

Name: 200 liter concrete mixer
Model: Electric Semi-Automatic 200 Litre Mini Concrete Mixer
Description: Electric 200-litre drum mixer for consistent batches on small to medium pours. Great for footings, slabs, and blockwork; keeps crews moving with fast, even mixing. Durable drum and straightforward controls for hassle-free operation.

Name: Hole boring machine
Description: Petrol post hole digger for quick and clean fence and footing holes. 63 cc engine with 200 mm auger works far faster than manual digging, even in firm ground. Supplied with extension and bits ideal for fence posts, pergolas, decks, and tree planting on residential sites and small farms.

Name: ZZZ Internal Test Machine (€1 - Do Not Rent)
Description: Internal listing to verify Stripe production checkout. Not available for hire. Charges kept at €1/day with a €1 deposit for testing; remove after validation.
